         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8286"> </a>Starting the screws (1) of the cable grommets (2) to position the rear brake hose and speed sensor cable on the swingarm.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8288"> </a>Reinstall the top grommet (B) and start screw (A).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8290"> </a>Tighten the screw (A) to a torque of 5 Nm ±10% and the screw (1) to a torque of 8 Nm ±10%.
         </div>
