         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8301"> </a>Locate the swinging arm (3) on the frame.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8303"> </a>Lubricate the swingarm shaft (4) and screw (5) with recommended grease and insert shaft fully into the frame.
         </div>
      </div>
