         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8310"> </a>Working on bike opposite side, smear screw (5) with recommended grease and use it to fasten the swingarm shaft (4), fit the
            washer (6) between the swingarm and the frame.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8312"> </a>Tighten screw (5) to a torque of 72 Nm ±5%.
